  "doc_id": "9423",
  "text": "Functional annotation of the genetic variants from the targeted resequencing was performed using the software Gemini (V.0.18.3) and snpEff (V.3.6). The associations between each variant and lung cancer risk were calculated using logistic regression model with adjustment for age, sex and smoking statue in PLINK (V.1.07). Conditional analysis was performed using an approximated joint regression model in GCTA [CITATION_1] to select index variants in 5p15.33 region, and those with nominal evidence of association (p < 0.05) were selected for further validation in multiple GWAS data sets.",
